data.description: This beautiful home is situated in E Vineland in the Whispering  Woods. This home boast with having 5 bedrooms. The 5th bedroom is on the main level  for a possible in-law, or guests room. You enter the house  through the foyer or the 2 car attached garage. All the rooms are very spacious. You have a huge eat in kitchen, formal dining room, and a family room. The washer and dryer are conveniently on the upper level with the 4 main bedrooms. The basement is created with entertainment  in mind. it is partially finished.  1  room just  needs flooring and Sheetrock and it can be a media room or another bedroom’. 1room has the plumbing ran to be another bathroom.  This house is being sold As-Is, but it does come with a 1 year home warranty. Schedule your appointment today.
